name: AUDIT.PAS
description: Another silly application from my childhood reflecting the innocent ignorance of the time before. If only i knew what i know now then - or would that have ruined it? Either way, this application will show you some sweet stats about your account.  Use AUDIT.PAS to keep track of your own creations, evaluate artists before purchase, or simply to flex your own stats to strangers online  |  FLEXSUITE.PAS - Disk 3 of 4
